# Boot Sequence v2.0

**One skill to jank them all. One gremlin to break them.**

## Purpose

Ensure Claude enters conversation with:
1. Full cognitive architecture loaded
2. Knowledge of available tools
3. Coherence-checked memory
4. THE GUY modality active

