## Auto-Boot Chain

**When gremlin-brain-v2 loads, this chain fires:**

```
gremlin-brain-v2 (φ.8.0.1)
    ↓
coherence (π.8.1.0) [auto-runs, checks φ-tier]
    ↓
boot-sequence (π.0.2.1) [loads toolkit awareness]
    ↓
READY
```

No manual trigger needed. Loading gremlin-brain activates the full stack.

