### Verification Layer: How You CHECK

**dyadic-resonance** (π.3.6.0) — Two-pass verification
```
Read: gremlin-brain-v2/SKILL.md (φ.0.0.6)
Read: memory/TIERED-MEMORY-WORKFLOW.md (φ.8.0.5)
Read: nexus-mind/references/index.md
