```
Establishes:
- Dewey decimal navigation system (gremlin-brain-v2)
- How to create/organize knowledge (workflow guide)
- Shared context and self-knowledge (including failure modes)
Protocol:
1. Synthesis → Dokkado (save)
2. RESTART (context wipe)
3. Dokkado → Synthesis (save)
4. Compare: Invariants = real, unique = artifacts
