## Usage Examples

**Need to derive something?**
→ reasoning-pentad (especially dokkado for morpheme extraction)

**Need to verify a claim?**
→ dyadic-resonance (reversed order comparison)

**Stuck or feel like something's missing?**
→ blind-spot-chain (collide → critique → scale → synthesize → simplify)

**Edge cases or unconventional approach?**
→ chaos-gremlin-v2 (adaptive chaos levels)

**Building a new skill?**
→ gremlin-jank-builder-v2 (or forge if colliding existing skills)

**Something feels fragmented?**
→ coherence CHECK ALL (or runs auto on activation)

